{# packs/events-management/templates/session-content-feedback.md.j2
   Jinja2 template for session content QC feedback emails to speakers.
   Rendered by session-content-qc agent.
   Sent autonomously (no HOTL gate) — feedback is constructive, non-financial.

   Context variables:
     speaker.name          — speaker full name
     session.title         — session title
     review.pass_status    — 'approved' | 'needs_revision'
     review.slide_score    — int 0–100
     review.abstract_score — int 0–100
     review.brand_score    — int 0–100 (null if brand guidelines not configured)
     review.feedback       — dict with keys: slides, abstract, brand (lists of strings)
     review.summary        — 1-2 sentence overall assessment
     resource_portal_url   — link to re-upload revised slides
     resubmit_deadline     — date by which revised materials should be submitted
     reviewer_name         — event team reviewer name for sign-off
#}

Subject: {% if review.pass_status == 'approved' %}
Your session content is approved — {{ session.title }}
{% else %}
Content review feedback for your session — {{ session.title }}
{% endif %}

---

Hi {{ speaker.name | first_name }},

{% if review.pass_status == 'approved' %}
Great news — your session materials for **{{ session.title }}** have passed
our content review.

{{ review.summary }}

You're all set! No further action is needed before the event. We will be in
touch with logistics closer to the date.
{% else %}
Thank you for submitting your materials for **{{ session.title }}**. Our
content team has completed an initial review and has a few suggestions to
help make your session even stronger.

{{ review.summary }}

---

**Review Scores**

| Dimension       | Score | Status |
|-----------------|:-----:|--------|
| Slides          | {{ review.slide_score }}/100 | {% if review.slide_score >= 70 %}✅ Pass{% else %}⚠️ Needs attention{% endif %} |
| Abstract        | {{ review.abstract_score }}/100 | {% if review.abstract_score >= 70 %}✅ Pass{% else %}⚠️ Needs attention{% endif %} |
{% if review.brand_score is not none %}
| Brand alignment | {{ review.brand_score }}/100 | {% if review.brand_score >= 70 %}✅ Pass{% else %}⚠️ Needs attention{% endif %} |
{% endif %}

---

{% if review.feedback.slides %}
**Slide feedback**

{% for item in review.feedback.slides %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

{% endif %}
{% if review.feedback.abstract %}
**Abstract feedback**

{% for item in review.feedback.abstract %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

{% endif %}
{% if review.brand_score is not none and review.feedback.brand %}
**Brand alignment feedback**

{% for item in review.feedback.brand %}
- {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

{% endif %}

---

**Next step:** Please upload your revised materials via the Speaker Resource
Portal by **{{ resubmit_deadline | date_format('%B %-d, %Y') }}**:

[Upload revised materials →]({{ resource_portal_url }})

Our team will re-review within 3 business days. If you have questions about
any of the feedback above, reply to this email.
{% endif %}

Warm regards,
{{ reviewer_name }}
Events Content Team
